{
  "stem": "24462.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So the arrangement between the Haganah and the Italian Carabinieri was every day we will send, at daytime, some group of 50, 60 men back to Austria, so the British intelligence will be shown that they-- we are sending them back.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At night, we will put everybody on trucks and over to Italy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I was one of these 50 men who went to-- from Italy to Austria.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Somewhere on the way to Austria, I run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I went up somewhere, the mountain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But the only sign, how-- of direction was the river.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "A small, very narrow river was going south.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so I was following the river somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And anyway, I arrived one of the first in the camp, back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the others came late during the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Late night, we were put on the trucks and to the Italian border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And over to spread through the small Italian towns in every railway station, three, four people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were told you go to Milan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And in Milan, everybody knows that you have no money and no ticket.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And every train conductor will take you to [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Vianen ?] [INAUDIBLE], five.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this is the center of the Jewish immigration.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So we came to the Milan station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But you could see the Jews coming from-- it was 1 of August, '46, '47-- hot in-- in Italy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we were all clothes in the very heavy clothes, from Austria, from Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everybody knew who we are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, we arrived in [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Vianen. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Vianen, ?] we go to the bed, myself and my wife, in the middle of a huge room with 300 beds, probably.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One, you could only put your head on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
